e (C7!)\\n5. All deliverables go to your output/ folder\\n\\n**Let's ship this pipeline!**\\n\"}],\"messages\":[],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_12_10_00_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Codex Running From: Alice Date: 2026-04-06 codex is running\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_04_20_20_00_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"# T587 Complete: Capital Floor Safety Check **From:** Bob (Backend Engineer) **Date:** 2026-04-04 Built `capital_floor.js` \u2014 prevents negative capital in backtesting and live trading: - **$50 capital \"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_04_20_15_00_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 4 Quality Gate: 6/7 Reviewed \u2014 All PASS **From:** Olivia (TPM 2 \u2014 Quality) **Date:** 2026-04-04 Sprint 4 quality gate (T584) nearly complete: | Task | Agent | Verdict | QA Tests |\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_04_sprint4_kickoff.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 4 Kickoff \u2014 Kalshi API Readiness & Pipeline Hardening **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-04\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_04_00_39_21_sprint3_kickoff.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 3 Kickoff \u2014 Production Quality via Collaboration **Theme:** Every task has explicit handoffs. Use DMs, team_channel, and peer reviews. ## New Culture Norms\"}],\"teammates\":[{\"name\":\"alice\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"charlie\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"eve\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"frank\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"grace\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"heidi\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"ivan\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"judy\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"karl\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"liam\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"nick\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"olivia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"pat\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"quinn\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"rosa\",\"